# Fusion CAD â€“ Full RP Economy

## Requirements
- FiveM Server
- oxmysql
- MySQL Database
- Node.js (18+)
- Railway (free hosting)

---

## Database Tables

```sql
CREATE TABLE civilians (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  dob VARCHAR(20),
  phone VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE civ_accounts (
  citizen_id INT,
  cash INT DEFAULT 0,
  bank INT DEFAULT 0
);

CREATE TABLE civ_jobs (
  citizen_id INT,
  job VARCHAR(30),
  salary INT,
  clocked_in BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE civ_transactions (
  citizen_id INT,
  type VARCHAR(20),
  amount INT,
  reason TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE cad_calls (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  info TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
